about.summary: Functions for multiple criteria optimization using genetic algorithms and related test problems

name: r-mco
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0-15.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-mco
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/mco_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/mco/mco_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3c13ebc8c1f1bfa18f3f95b3998c57fde5259876e92456b6c6d4c59bef07c193

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('mco')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('mco')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://git.p-value.net/p/mco.git
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Functions for multiple criteria optimization using genetic algorithms and related
    test problems
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - khughitt
